image_analysis.description: This is an image of a completed OGE Form 278e, a public financial disclosure report. This specific page is Part 6, detailing 'Other Assets and Income' for the filer, Donald J. Trump. The page is numbered 34 of 51 and lists various funds, bank accounts, and stock holdings with their corresponding values and income amounts in ranges. The information is reported as of April 15, 2017.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a standard form layout. A header contains the form title, instructions, filer's name, and page number. The main body consists of a large table with columns for item number, description, EIF, value, income type, and income amount. A footer at the bottom provides the reporting date and a document identification number.
